lead_paragraph: Washington Redskins cornerback Josh Norman was fined $48,620 by the NFL on Friday for his unnecessary roughness foul on New York Giants wide receiver Sterling Shepard last week.

headline.print_headline: Redskins' Norman Fined $48,620 for Hit vs. Giants Receiver
